<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Can you feel empathy for a dancing robot?</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resImageText section">


























		<div class="row" id="941016f1-1732-475a-b09a-9b32123fc1a9">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					
<img src="/content/dam/research/images/newsletter/2020-07/dancing-robot-0.jpg" alt="An onlooker records a performer dancing with a large mechanical arm with their smart phone"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>The Uncanny Robots project’s first production, involving a robot arm and dancer Belinda McGuire, was premiered at the launch of the Creative Technology Lab. Photo courtesy of the Faculty of Communication and Design.</p>
</div>
						    
					
